🏳️‍🌈 Givenchy Beauty is releasing a new NFT to support MAG Jeunes.

MAG Jeunes is an association of young lesbian, gay, bi and trans people aged 15 to 30. It welcomes all the people who pass the door of its premises and proposes them activities of conviviality, cultural and militant. Its role is also to prevent and fight against LGBTphobia.

On sale tonight, 9pm Paris time.

@mag_jeunes_lgbt @rwd_collective @amarsinghgallery @veve.digital.collectibles
#givenchybeauty #nft #artwork #pride

🏳️‍🌈 « PRIDE ll », Non-Fungible Token by Rewind Collective and Amar Gallery for Mag Jeunes. 

This digital artwork is available for sale as an NFT at @veve.digital.collectibles tonight 9pm Paris Time  – All of the proceeds will be donated to the association. 

@mag_jeunes_lgbt @rwd_collective @amarsinghgallery 
#givenchybeauty #nft #artwork #pride

🏳️‍🌈 Givenchy Beauty issues its second NFT for #PrideMonth2022.

This year, we renewed our Partnership with @rwd_collective and @amarsinghgallery to create a new NFT honoring the fight for LGBTQIA+ rights around the world. The digital artwork will be sold today 9pm Paris Time, in an exclusive online sale at @veve.digital.collectibles and all of the proceeds will be donated to @mag_jeunes_lgbt to help them in their exceptional work.

#givenchybeauty #nft #artwork #pride
